    next js : 直接加你想要的页面的js文件就好
routes会直接加进去

    npm install next。。。。
    记得改package。json
    npm run dev

    link： <link herf = "/shows">
                <a>name</a>// any type of html tag. button p a 均可
            </link>

    Wraping pages:
        /components/header.js
        exprot default header
        然后在pages里边的js页面里用<Header/>就好

    My layout
        /components/MyLayOut.js
        export default MyLayOut;
        index里用就好，还要import
    
    link option: <link as=.... herf =....>
        as用于隐藏query string
        but as is client side, sever dont know what as content link 
        Therefore we need to write some js(server.js)

        also package.json, we used to use "dev":"next"
        change to "dev": "node server.js"

    Styling:
        js中写<style jsx> css stuff </style>  

        global style:
        copy paste to layout.js
        and set jsx= global in <style jsx=global>

    总体来说就是快+好写     

    